<!channel> - as we head into the week, please keep in mind that I’m in LA Wednesday - Friday. I should be able to export new times of the song pending final timing. But I won’t be able to record any new stuff, much less spend a ton of time dedicated to it while out of town. 

That’s the one bottleneck that I know I present this week. As much as possible, I’d love to plan ahead for that. 

Thanks in advance, and I can’t wait to ship this thing!
